name: Train
description:
Print of my illustration "Train". The original is a hand painted watercolour.

Printed on an uncoated 300gsm paper, 26"(w) x 10"(h).

Prints will be sent rolled in postal tubes.

UK orders will be sent via recorded delivery

Whilst I will endeavor to get your items sent out to you within 3 working days, please allow up to 14 days for delivery on UK orders. At the moment currently only shipping to the UK, no oversea's orders, sorry.
